{"word":"Jonathan","slug":"jonathan","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jonathan</b> <a href=\"#/H3083\">H3083</a><br/><a href=\"#/H3129\">H3129</a> <br/> 1. A Levite of Bethlehem, who becomes a priest for Micah; accepts idolatry; joins the Danites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=17&verse=13'>Jdg 17:13</a>; <a href='B:'></a><br/> 2. Son of Saul:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=49'>1Sa 14:49</a> <br/> - Victory of:<br/> b Over the Philistine garrison of Geba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=4'>1Sa 13:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=16'>1Sa 13:16</a><br/> b Over Philistines at Michmash<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=18'>1Sa 14:18</a><br/> - Under Saul's curse pronounced against any who might take food before he was avenged of his enemies<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=30'>1Sa 14:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=43'>1Sa 14:43</a> <br/> - Rescued by the people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=45'>1Sa 14:45</a> <br/> - Love of, for David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=4'>1Sa 18:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=7'>1Sa 19:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=20'>1Sa 20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=23&verse=18'>1Sa 23:18</a> <br/> - Killed in battle with Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=2'>1Sa 31:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=6'>1Sa 31:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=10&verse=2'>1Ch 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=21&verse=14'>2Sa 21:14</a> <br/> - Buried by inhabitants of Jabesh-Gilead<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=13'>1Sa 31:13</a> <br/> - Mourned by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Sa 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=27'>2Sa 1:27</a> <br/> - Son of, cared for by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=4&verse=4'>2Sa 4:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=9&verse=13'>2Sa 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=34'>1Ch 8:34</a> <br/> 3. Son of Abiathar:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=27'>2Sa 15:27</a> <br/> - Acts as spy for David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=28'>2Sa 15:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=22'>2Sa 17:22</a> <br/> - Informs Adonijah of Solomon's succession to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=48'>1Ki 1:48</a> <br/> 4. Nephew of David, slays a giant, and becomes one of David's chief warriors<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=21&verse=21'>2Sa 21:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=20&verse=7'>1Ch 20:7</a><br/> 5. One of David's heroes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=32'>2Sa 23:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=34'>1Ch 11:34</a><br/> 6. A son of Jada<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=33'>1Ch 2:33</a><br/> 7. Secretary of the cabinet of David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=32'>1Ch 27:32</a><br/> 8. Father of Ebed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=6'>Ezr 8:6</a><br/> 9. Son of Asahel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=15'>Ezr 10:15</a><br/> 10. Called Johanan, a descendant of Jeshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=11'>Neh 12:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=22'>Neh 12:22</a><br/> 11. Name of two priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=14'>Neh 12:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=35'>Neh 12:35</a><br/> 12. A scribe<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=15'>Jer 37:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=20'>Jer 37:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=26'>Jer 38:26</a><br/> 13. Son of Kareah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=40&verse=8'>Jer 40:8</a>"}]}